<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ZeroSite Expert Edition v21 Professional - {{ address }}</title>
    
    {# Import v21 Professional CSS Design System #}
    <style>
        {% include "v21_css_professional.css" %}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {# Import v21 UI Component Macros - TEMPORARILY DISABLED FOR TESTING #}
    {# % import "v21_layout_components.html" as ui % #}
    
    {# ================================================================
       COVER PAGE - Professional LH Blue Design
       ================================================================ #}
    <div class="cover-page">
        <div class="cover-header">
            <img src="https://www.lh.or.kr/resources/images/common/logo.png" alt="LH 로고" class="lh-logo" style="height: 60px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 28pt; color: var(--lh-primary); margin: 20px 0;">
                ZeroSite Expert Edition v21
            </h1>
            <h2 style="font-size: 20pt; color: var(--lh-gray-dark); margin: 15px 0; font-weight: 400;">
                LH 공공주택 사업 타당성 분석 보고서
            </h2>
            <div class="cover-subtitle" style="font-size: 14pt; color: var(--lh-gray-medium); margin: 30px 0;">
                McKinsey-Grade Professional Report
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="cover-content" style="margin-top: 80px;">
            <div class="project-info-card" style="background: var(--lh-light-bg); padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 6px solid var(--lh-primary);">
                <h3 style="color: var(--lh-primary); font-size: 16pt; margin-bottom: 25px;">📍 대상 사업지 정보</h3>
                <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 2.0;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="color: var(--lh-gray-medium); width: 150px;">주소</td>
                        <td style="color: var(--lh-gray-dark); font-weight: 600;">{{ address }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="color: var(--lh-gray-medium);">대지 면적</td>
